QuestData.Title: Seek the Wind Serpent Goddess
QuestData.Description: You are prepared, but I'm not certain that you're ready for what is to come.$B$BWhen you cross back over into Quetz'lun's altar area, you will enter the realm of the dead. From what I can feel of it, it's not going to be pleasant.$B$BTry not to be distracted by what you see in there. Simply head for the altar building and seek out Quetz'lun's Spirit.
QuestData.LogDescription: Seek Quetz'lun's Spirit at the Altar of Quetz'lun.
QuestData.RewardText: $R worm. Tell me why I should not annihilate you where you stand?
